=== 官方使用 ===
《叢林流浪》從未被官方認定為[[澳洲國歌|澳洲國歌]]，但在一些場合上被當作國歌般使用。

1977年，澳洲{{tsl|en|Australian plebiscite, 1977 (National Song)||舉行公投確立國歌}}，《叢林流浪》作為選項之一，獲得了28%的選票，超越《[[天佑女王|天佑女王]]》（19%）和《澳洲之歌》（{{tsl|en|Song of Australia||Song of Australia}}）（10%），但不敵《[[前進澳洲美之國|前進澳洲美之國]]》的43%。<ref name="1977SongPoll">{{cite web | year = 2002 | url = http://www.aph.gov.au/library/elect/referend/pleb.htm | title = Plebiscite results – see 1977 National Song Poll | work = Elections and referendums | publisher = Department of the Parliament (Australian federal government) | accessdate = 21 November 2007 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071120035149/http://www.aph.gov.au/library/elect/referend/pleb.htm | archivedate = 2007-11-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2003年起，部分[[澳洲护照|澳洲護照]]內頁以微型字體印有《叢林流浪》的歌詞。<ref>{{cite news |title= Passport gets the hop on fraudsters |url= http://edition.cnn.com/2003/WORLD/asiapcf/auspac/11/27/australia.passport/ |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20031207182218/http://edition.cnn.com/2003/WORLD/asiapcf/auspac/11/27/australia.passport/ |archivedate= 2003-12-07 |accessdate= 2020-02-18 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

===體育===
1982年英聯邦運動會在布里斯本舉行，其吉祥物就是名為「Matilda」的一隻袋鼠。在開幕儀式上，澳洲歌手羅爾夫·哈里斯（Rolf Harris）演唱《叢林流浪》歌曲，伴隨身高達13米的Matilda機械袋鼠出場。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/Sport/A-word-to-the-wise-guy/2005/04/08/1112815727746.html|title=A word to the wise guy – Sport|work=[[雪梨晨鋒報|雪梨晨鋒報]]|date=9 April 2005|accessdate=1 July 2009|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924194537/http://www.smh.com.au/news/Sport/A-word-to-the-wise-guy/2005/04/08/1112815727746.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

受此歌曲影響，[[澳大利亚国家女子足球队|澳洲國家女子足球隊]]成員被稱為「The Matildas」。<ref>{{cite web |author=Independent Online |url=http://www.iol.co.za/index.php?click_id=2822&art_id=vn20071027084136519C572802&set_id= |title=News – SA Soccer: If a name works, why fix it? |publisher=Iol.co.za |date=27 October 2007 |accessdate=1 July 2009 |archive-date=2009-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091221203818/http://www.iol.co.za/index.php?click_id=2822 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

